+Feature: Tidewatch station data
+
+  @captain
+  Scenario: Station lookup returns tide monitoring station metadata
+    Given the station registry is available
+    When a lookup for station "Fundy Cove 1" is made
+    Then the station is found with phaseOffset 116.58 and amplitudeScale 0.814
+
+  @captain
+  Scenario: Station lookup reports missing station
+    Given the station registry is available
+    When a lookup for station "Nonexistent Point" is made
+    Then the lookup fails with "station not found"
